	SameValueNonNumber: function SameValueNonNumber(x, y) {
		if (typeof x === 'number' || typeof x !== typeof y) {
			throw new TypeError('SameValueNonNumber requires two non-number values of the same type.');
		}
		return this.SameValue(x, y);
	}
});
